</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">If you renamed the wrong file, or named your file improperly, you can
    undo the rename. To revert the action, immediately click the menu button in
    the sidebar and select <span class="gui">Undo Rename</span>, or press
    <span class="keyseq"><span class="key"><kbd>Ctrl</kbd></span>+<span class="key"><kbd>Z</kbd></span></span>, to restore the former
    name.</p></div></div></div>
</div>
